  <summary date="2020-03-24T21:03:51Z" status="Introduced in House">12 Carrier Act

This bill requires the U.S. Navy to have no less than 12 operational aircraft carriers as part of its naval combat forces.

Presently, the Navy must have 11 such carriers.</summary>
